title: [Small Mammals]
[Small mammals]
description: The gravel-lined path bordered with fences overgrown with night blooming jasmine vines winds between two caged enclosures.  On one side of the path, a silvery mithril-barred enclosure houses a small bronze-clawed firecat.  Opposing the mithril enclosure is a glass-enclosed frozen tundra habitat.

The air is perfumed with the heavy scent of jasmine emanating from the open blooms along that cover the low fence bordering the path.
